口罩等同標籤自己，要街坊裝<br />\n3.如果要裝修可以去無cctv位，例如廁所換裝，做完要快閃<br />\n4.知道有便衣狗要打到佢地仆街，便衣唔同full gear，易打好多<br />\n5.便衣捉人要救人<br />\n6.個商場要人流多，多人做掩護<br />\n7.商場要夠大，出口要夠多<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"13a08df09ee4f2dcbaac0be504a2f8b3df092449","tid":1703780,"uid":76310,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"af265050239f09943c5521a588b3579f0220a310","tid":1703780,"uid":14422,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:48:04.000Z","msg":"唔裝修。拉你返去都告唔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:49:56.000Z","msg":"裝修風險大 未必走到<br />\n如果要裝 做完要即閃，唔好戀戰<br />\n商場夠大多出口先易逃生"},{"pid":"b964fdc468f71a8e7c20c38cbd137ec3c0f6b6ef","tid":1703780,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:51:20.000Z","msg":"值得"},{"pid":"983ffc6e4e1810e1acfa7e7dc570f0cabac1155e","tid":1703780,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:52:59.000Z","msg":"商場要多人流先可以做掩護，小人或者無人既會變困獸鬥"},{"pid":"0d51c08fb1fd50177955ddea6abbaa0930b68b42","tid":1703780,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:53:29.000Z","msg":"又一城今日係唔係大失敗？<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"ebeaf5dc1e8a7d9c762e61c90995fea463f579a5","tid":1703780,"uid":83015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"依<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ozoPcNL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FozoPcNL.png&h=020b03a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b00badc5e141d8de23d4210001518007a591070b","tid":1703780,"uid":26876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:54:53.000Z","msg":"值得<br />\n但講清楚目標 商鋪收鋪就閃Ok?<br />\n收商家皮比壓力佢地"},{"pid":"27bed81e182218b2abd37fcaeca417acc891ca5c","tid":1703780,"uid":279590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"聽日可能出現嘅情況<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/etMaAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_b